K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543a-30: 'du shes med 'du shes med min skye mched kyi lha rnams yod do ////
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-0: @543b ` de la lam shes mtshon byed kyi chos
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-1: bzhi pa mthong lam rgyas bshad skabs snar thang par
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-2: mar tshad med kyi 'gres rkang gcig las sdug bsngal
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-3: rjes bzod dang rjes shes kyi mdo so sor med
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-4: pa 'bum gyi gnod 'joms sogs dang mthun zhing /
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-5: de'ang tshad med kyi don tshad ma med pa dang /
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-6: chad [*tshad?] med pa gnyis ka la drang du rung bas yin nam snyam la /
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-7: sde dger de chad skyon du bsam ste rjes shes
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-8: kyi mdor dpag tu med pa'i mdo tshan zhig bcug
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-15: yum gsum mthun bstan rnams dang 'grig tsam yang /
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-17: la brgyad ma dang don gsal sogs rgya gzhung tshad thub rnams dang 'gal bar snang la /
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-18: lhag par gong gi gzhung drug po de la gser
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-19: phreng sogs su rje yab sras kyis dgag brjod yang
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-20: yang mdzad phyir dag gtugs kyi khungs su mi che
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-21: bas da res dpag med dor zhing /
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-22: tshad med kyi don gnyis su 'gyur bas don la
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-23: 'gal ba med pa de lta na'ang brgyad stong par
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-25: tshad med pa'i mdo so sor mdzad pa ltar mngon rtogs rgyan du'ang tshad ma med bcas dang /
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-26: tshad med pa dang zhes tshad ma med pa logs su gsungs la /
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-27: de bzhin du 'phags seng gi gzhung snang ba gnyis
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-28: sogs rgya 'grel nyer gcig tu grags pa'i nang tshan
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-29: mdo rgyan sbyar phal cher dang /
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-30: bod kyi mkhas pa bu ston /
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-32: rje yab sras sogs tshad ldan gyi gzhung rnams mgrin
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:543b-33: gcig tu dpag med dor te rjes bzod la tshad
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:544a-1: pa'i mdo so sor 'dren par mdzad 'dug pa bzhin
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:544a-2: 'jug pa bde ba'i phyir glegs bam 'dir tshad ma
K02D0008-5_H0009-5:544a-3: med pa'i 'gres rkang gsar du bcug pa la gzur
